  <div style="background-color: #e8ecfb; padding: 0.5em 1em 0.5em 1.5em;">
    <h1>Attach Files to the Message</h1>
<p>List added files under <code>attachments</code> frontmatter section.
Images are automatically compressed. Control the size
with <code>media_constraints</code> frontmatter section.</p>
<h2>Inline Attachments</h2>
<p>Inline attachments are placed into message body,
when linked like so: <a href="../internal/media/testdata/cat.jpg" title="Cat Photo by Cindy vanHeerden">cat</a>.</p>
